&lt;li&gt;Model electrical cross-talk and optimize electronic-photonic integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop RF back-end-of-line (BEOL) stack designs, focusing on signal integrity and minimal loss.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
