&lt;li&gt;Automate and script simulations with Python or similar languages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with team members using Git for code management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate photonic designs into system architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
