&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MSc in Photonics, Electrical Engineering, or related; PhD preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in photonic and optoelectronic design, preferably in industry (academic research considered)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with EO material design and simulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Lumerical and PIC layout tools (eg. IPKISS, GdsFactory).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Python skills and experience with Git.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in English.&lt;/li&gt;
